{"tid":2218665,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［Gphone] ‘元祖級手足‘ 「蠔涌爆炸品案」罪成出獄後 彭艾烈開咗間意大利食材網店Rizzy Italia","createTime":"2020-09-26T11:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T12:50:30.000Z","uid":48083,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7d226e7b6281fcec0094fe426b34e93f21f3ea86","tid":2218665,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T11:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9c5wfOB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9c5wfOB.png&h=7363cab7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒 Joshua Wong<br />\n彭艾烈（Rizzy Pennelli）可謂「元祖級手足」，早在連「火魔法」這個名詞也未存在的年代，他已因「蠔涌爆炸品案」被判串謀製造炸藥和管有炸藥罪成，入獄服刑3年10個月。<br />\n<br />\n離開監獄以後，他經營意大利食材網購店，同時以過來人的身份與社福機構合作，開班授徒舉辦健身工作坊，讓社會知悉即使曾因與政治有關案件身陷囹圄，￼￼￼也可有一番作為。<br />\n<br />\n有關他的心路歷程，有興趣可自行細閱明報人物專訪，￼￼而在這裏當然就是希望跟大家推介Rizzy Italia - 意大利仔的佳餚食材店，￼以及Rizzy Pennelli，我也會在下廚後寫寫食評～<br />\n<br />\n#黃之鋒撐黃店￼<br />\n<br />\n因蠔涌爆炸品案坐牢 瘦仔變健碩 獄中健身自強 釋囚組過來人教練團<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20200830/s00002\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200830%2Fs00002&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu2E7lpprR278wgWha8tNVfY%3D&h=55aec672\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200830%2Fs00002&h=d0609fcb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20200830/s00002</a><br />\n<br />\n父子檔經營意大利食品生意 變親子活動<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20200830/s00002/1598724707461\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200830%2Fs00002%2F1598724707461&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu2E7lpprR278wgWha8tNVfY%3D&h=21b3cf9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200830%2Fs00002%2F1598724707461&h=d8d63705\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20200830/s00002/1598724707461</a><br />\n<br />\n．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．<br />\n💪支持我向世界展現香港人頑強抵抗的意志：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/joshuawonghk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fjoshuawonghk&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu2E7lpprR278wgWha8tNVfY%3D&h=e262d045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/joshuawonghk</a><br />\n╭───────────────────╮<br />\n╞#存亡號召 #絕處逢生<br />\n╞🌐<a href=\"https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoshuawongcf&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu2E7lpprR278wgWha8tNVfY%3D&h=fa246be6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf</a><br />\n╞📷<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/joshua1013\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fjoshua1013&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu2E7lpprR278wgWha8tNVfY%3D&h=35aca08a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/joshua1013</a><br />\n╞📧joshua@joshuawongcf.com<br />\n╰───────────────────╯"},{"pid":"2d7b42b8600c539fe67be9cd4b4cf257b7ceba64","tid":2218665,"uid":48947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T11:20:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6bb3b862ee378a8ad025f408ca9798911802151","tid":2218665,"uid":55197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T11:32:36.000Z","msg":"推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5abd90f0c8282486b53c35ce717bc9c1852bd05b","tid":2218665,"uid":132554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T11:39:24.000Z","msg":"呢個要推俾更多人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c5559391952ec7bfd89b69412d42db8862da65b","tid":2218665,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T11:41:44.000Z","